{"tid":2025643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺講起黃色經濟圈嘅時候，好似總係冇乜人提Boyz Reborn？","createTime":"2020-05-20T11:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T12:16:06.000Z","uid":227650,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6f0a64d0146916ea5e9878bea1de3d8fbabbda04","tid":2025643,"uid":227650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T11:27:25.000Z","msg":"講起黃色經濟圈嘅時候，好似總係冇乜人提boyz reborn咁。<br />\n<br />\n對我嚟講，佢哋算係一隊黃到發金嘅band。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋喺2014年已經有出關於政治嘅歌<br />\n<br />\n「青年人寫歌，並非只有「情情塔塔」。下月將開演唱會的Boyz Reborn，歌曲除談及學業，亦談政治。2014年佔領運動，Boyz Reborn先後重唱《問誰未發聲》及《撐起雨傘》，並自創歌曲《催淚彈》，YouTube點撃率達二十多萬。Boyz Reborn並非「抽抽水」，繼續推出政治歌曲；更為了繼續唱政治歌，推卻演唱會贊助。」<br />\n<br />\n經理人Eddie認為「音樂係關於人嘅生活，政治就係人嘅生活，所以音樂應該都要有政治」。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋呢幾日都出咗首關於政治嘅歌《#younglivesmatter》<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3rcGkGm2LNQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3rcGkGm2LNQ&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krOr6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=4f83375c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3rcGkGm2LNQ</a><br />\n<br />\nbtw,我好鍾意佢哋首《給青春的你》同埋《那年十八》<br />\n<br />\n請大家多多支持呢隊band"},{"pid":"3402bacf0a147fa8107e74cd520027a77603c1ee","tid":2025643,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T11:28:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db29c7444ae464a44b1e03fc18112a236c8d7dd9","tid":2025643,"uid":227650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T11:29:05.000Z","msg":"我冇開錯台，係真係想開喺時事台。"},{"pid":"758540a32f5b3f5c111f512893edccbdfb8895f6","tid":2025643,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T11:35:21.000Z","msg":"會留意下"},{"pid":"3662590c8db04e73471026bb5168f6e6cfc93a59","tid":2025643,"uid":227650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T11:45:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bdff071caa89d63f06637dafa5686d0b126a3738","tid":2025643,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T11:47:34.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"9642069a5f7c65d41